title: Galette des Rois Recipe for De'Longhi MultiFry
description:
Learn how to prepare delicious Galette des Rois with your De’Longhi MultiFry. Please note that adding the porcelain bean is a tradition but can be removed from the recipe as required. For more information please visit the links below:
